WEBVTT

00:57:12.000 --> 00:57:15.999
Come join Noline.

00:57:16.000 --> 00:57:17.999
Hyung, you'll need to put it in writing.

00:57:18.000 --> 00:57:18.999
In writing?

00:57:19.000 --> 00:57:19.999
Yes, I have a...

00:57:20.000 --> 00:57:21.999
Do we really need to go that far?

00:57:22.000 --> 00:57:24.999
That's a little too strict.

00:57:25.000 --> 00:57:25.999
Understood.

00:57:26.000 --> 00:57:27.999
There's also a contract deposit involved...

00:57:28.000 --> 00:57:28.999
A deposit too?

00:57:29.000 --> 00:57:30.999
Just a modest one, of course.

00:57:31.000 --> 00:57:31.999
Right.

00:57:32.000 --> 00:57:32.999
If you want to join Noline...

00:57:33.000 --> 00:57:35.999
Hamin is fine.

00:57:36.000 --> 00:57:36.999
He's always...

00:57:37.000 --> 00:57:37.999
Why is Hamin exempt?

00:57:38.000 --> 00:57:39.999
Hamin always tells me...

00:57:40.000 --> 00:57:41.999
how grateful he is.

00:57:42.000 --> 00:57:43.999
Right, right.

00:57:44.000 --> 00:57:45.999
So I consider his deposit paid.

00:57:46.000 --> 00:57:46.999
That's how I see it.

00:57:47.000 --> 00:57:49.999
I never got one, obviously.

00:57:50.000 --> 00:57:52.999
I didn't even know I'd joined Noline.
I just found myself in it.

00:57:53.000 --> 00:57:55.999
Okay, understood.

00:57:56.000 --> 00:57:56.999
All right, settled.

00:58:17.000 --> 00:58:18.999
Now, for the segment we prepared today...

00:58:19.000 --> 00:58:20.999
There's a reason the producer line is here.

00:58:21.000 --> 00:58:21.999
Right, right, right.

00:58:22.000 --> 00:58:23.999
Everyone, you know this one, right?

00:58:24.000 --> 00:58:27.999
Challenge, Heaven!

00:58:28.000 --> 00:58:29.999
Challenge, Heaven!

00:58:30.000 --> 00:58:33.999
Wow, your line really plays along well.

00:58:34.000 --> 00:58:36.999
You really are different.

00:58:37.000 --> 00:58:39.999
You're genuinely different aliens.

00:58:40.000 --> 00:58:40.999
I admit it.

00:58:41.000 --> 00:58:41.999
Was that hard to play along with?

00:58:42.000 --> 00:58:42.999
No, hyung. We know exactly what to do.

00:58:43.000 --> 00:58:44.999
It was just so sudden.

00:58:45.000 --> 00:58:45.999
When he said, ‘Challenge, Heaven!’

00:58:46.000 --> 00:58:46.999
I wondered how I was supposed to respond.

00:58:47.000 --> 00:58:48.999
That's what I was thinking.

00:58:49.000 --> 00:58:49.999
Then, right beside me...

00:58:50.000 --> 00:58:50.999
he was already going, ‘Wooo!’

00:58:51.000 --> 00:58:52.999
You can't stop to think then.

00:58:53.000 --> 00:58:54.999
The moment he says ‘Heaven’...

00:58:55.000 --> 00:58:56.999
you trust that he has a plan.

00:58:57.000 --> 00:58:57.999
You have to empty your mind.

00:58:58.000 --> 00:58:59.999
Just go with it.

00:59:00.000 --> 00:59:00.999
Yes—just charge ahead.

00:59:01.000 --> 00:59:01.999
Excellent.

00:59:02.000 --> 00:59:03.999
I learned something new today.

00:59:04.000 --> 00:59:05.999
What song will we make
for Challenge, Heaven today?

00:59:06.000 --> 00:59:06.999
For Challenge, Heaven...

00:59:07.000 --> 00:59:08.999
we'll make another new song.

00:59:09.000 --> 00:59:09.999
Are we really going to make a thousand?

00:59:10.000 --> 00:59:15.999
A producer-line broadcast proving
we could make a thousand songs.

00:59:16.000 --> 00:59:20.999
Remember the song Yejun-hyung
and I made on stream?

00:59:21.000 --> 00:59:22.999
Noah-hyung wasn't there that time.

00:59:23.000 --> 00:59:24.999
We mentioned this then too.

00:59:25.000 --> 00:59:27.999
The plan was for hyung to make verse two...

00:59:28.000 --> 00:59:33.999
finish it, assign the parts,
and turn it into a complete song.

00:59:34.000 --> 00:59:34.999
Hyung, did you watch it, at least?

00:59:35.000 --> 00:59:35.999
Of course I did.

00:59:36.000 --> 00:59:37.999
Yejun and I even made choreography for it.

00:59:38.000 --> 00:59:38.999
Yes, we made choreography too.

00:59:39.000 --> 00:59:39.999
Right, right, right.

00:59:40.000 --> 00:59:40.999
I saw that. I did.

00:59:41.000 --> 00:59:41.999
We made choreography too.

00:59:42.000 --> 00:59:42.999
So...

00:59:43.000 --> 00:59:43.999
instead of developing that song further...

00:59:44.000 --> 00:59:46.999
Yes, exactly.

00:59:47.000 --> 00:59:47.999
we brought something new.

00:59:48.000 --> 00:59:48.999
Right. We thought, why not make a new one?

00:59:49.000 --> 00:59:49.999
Right.

00:59:50.000 --> 00:59:52.999
That's why we brought this.

00:59:53.000 --> 00:59:54.999
For today's segment...

00:59:55.000 --> 00:59:55.999
That's right.

00:59:56.000 --> 00:59:56.999
we prepared a completely new track.

00:59:57.000 --> 00:59:57.999
We brought one.

00:59:58.000 --> 00:59:58.999
We did.

00:59:59.000 --> 01:00:00.999
It's extremely rough right now, though.

01:00:01.000 --> 01:00:02.999
We deliberately kept it rough.

01:00:03.000 --> 01:00:03.999
Completely rough.

01:00:04.000 --> 01:00:05.999
Just a first sketch.

01:00:06.000 --> 01:00:06.999
Honestly, it's embarrassing.

01:00:07.000 --> 01:00:07.999
We brought the very first draft.

01:00:08.000 --> 01:00:10.999
We're revealing it despite the embarrassment.

01:00:11.000 --> 01:00:11.999
We want to show you the real process.

01:00:12.000 --> 01:00:12.999
Right, right.

01:00:13.000 --> 01:00:16.999
This truly is just the sketch stage.

01:00:17.000 --> 01:00:17.999
We want you to keep that in mind.

01:00:18.000 --> 01:00:18.999
Right.

01:00:19.000 --> 01:00:20.999
If what we make today turns out well...

01:00:21.000 --> 01:00:21.999
Yes.

01:00:22.000 --> 01:00:23.999
we can develop it further.

01:00:24.000 --> 01:00:24.999
Right. That could happen.

01:00:25.000 --> 01:00:26.999
But if it isn't good today...

01:00:27.000 --> 01:00:27.999
we might throw it straight in the trash.

01:00:28.000 --> 01:00:28.999
That could happen too.

01:00:29.000 --> 01:00:30.999
We have to be ruthless.

01:00:31.000 --> 01:00:31.999
If it isn't good...

01:00:32.000 --> 01:00:33.999
we've ruthlessly trashed plenty of songs.

01:00:34.000 --> 01:00:34.999
A lot.

01:00:35.000 --> 01:00:35.999
So many. There are really so many.

01:00:36.000 --> 01:00:36.999
If you drag it out...

01:00:37.000 --> 01:00:37.999
This is how I see it.

01:00:38.000 --> 01:00:39.999
If you overthink it for too long...

01:00:40.000 --> 01:00:40.999
it isn't good.

01:00:41.000 --> 01:00:42.999
It won't come.
A good song won't come out.

01:00:43.000 --> 01:00:46.999
The spark has to appear
within the first few tries.

01:00:47.000 --> 01:00:47.999
Right, right.

01:00:48.000 --> 01:00:49.999
If you keep clinging to it...

01:00:50.000 --> 01:00:51.999
you're better off making something new.

01:00:52.000 --> 01:00:52.999
Right. That's true.

01:00:53.000 --> 01:00:53.999
It's better to start something new.

01:00:54.000 --> 01:00:54.999
Right, right.

01:00:55.000 --> 01:00:59.999
So we brought this track...

01:01:00.000 --> 01:01:01.999
to show you that process as a full group.

01:01:02.000 --> 01:01:03.999
That's what we prepared.

01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:07.999
Actually, while we were preparing this...

01:01:08.000 --> 01:01:09.999
I wondered if we should at least...

01:01:10.000 --> 01:01:12.999
organize it a little before coming here.

01:01:13.000 --> 01:01:13.999
Right, right.

01:01:14.000 --> 01:01:16.999
I said that to both of them.

01:01:17.000 --> 01:01:19.999
Shouldn't we at least work out...

01:01:20.000 --> 01:01:21.999
how should I put it—the foundation?

01:01:22.000 --> 01:01:24.999
I thought we needed some foundation
before we could work here.

01:01:25.000 --> 01:01:26.999
But both of them said...

01:01:27.000 --> 01:01:27.999
we had to do it genuinely live.

01:01:28.000 --> 01:01:28.999
Exactly. It has to be real.

01:01:29.000 --> 01:01:30.999
It has to be completely real.

01:01:31.000 --> 01:01:31.999
Okay.

01:01:32.000 --> 01:01:32.999
Then let's do it that way.

01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:34.999
They convinced me immediately.

01:01:35.000 --> 01:01:35.999
It seemed like the right choice.

01:01:36.000 --> 01:01:37.999
So we may flounder and make nothing today.

01:01:38.000 --> 01:01:39.999
Viewers, are you watching?

01:01:40.000 --> 01:01:42.999
We're PLAVE, and we keep our streams real.

01:01:43.000 --> 01:01:43.999
Please enjoy the show.

01:01:44.000 --> 01:01:48.999
Please enjoy it.

01:01:49.000 --> 01:01:52.999
Get up.

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:53.999
What? What is it?

01:01:54.000 --> 01:01:55.999
What were you doing—calisthenics?

01:01:56.000 --> 01:01:56.999
Standing over here...

01:01:57.000 --> 01:01:57.999
What are you doing?

01:01:58.000 --> 01:01:58.999
What is this?

01:01:59.000 --> 01:01:59.999
Wait a second.

01:02:00.000 --> 01:02:00.999
I was warming up.

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:02.999
I saw you run over and wondered why.

01:02:03.000 --> 01:02:04.999
He must have been getting ready for that.

01:02:05.000 --> 01:02:06.999
I was preparing.
This is part of the preparation.

01:02:07.000 --> 01:02:07.999
I was getting ready.

01:02:08.000 --> 01:02:09.999
Why are you suddenly doing this?

01:02:10.000 --> 01:02:10.999
You came over here by yourself...

01:02:11.000 --> 01:02:11.999
Why are you suddenly standing like that?

01:02:12.000 --> 01:02:12.999
Jumping jacks.

01:02:13.000 --> 01:02:15.999
Wait—I was gathering my energy like this.

01:02:16.000 --> 01:02:17.999
I was gathering energy.

01:02:18.000 --> 01:02:20.999
Or maybe I could make this into a challenge.

01:02:21.000 --> 01:02:21.999
You were frozen in that pose?

01:02:22.000 --> 01:02:24.999
Like this?

01:02:25.000 --> 01:02:29.999
I was going to do something like this.

01:02:30.000 --> 01:02:32.999
Oh, honestly...

01:02:33.000 --> 01:02:37.999
You startled me.

01:02:38.000 --> 01:02:41.999
Since we're at home...

01:02:42.000 --> 01:02:42.999
I loosened up a little.

01:02:43.000 --> 01:02:45.999
I thought I was about to fly away, everyone.

01:02:46.000 --> 01:02:47.999
I thought you were Iron Man.

01:02:48.000 --> 01:02:48.999
That startled me.

01:58:08.000 --> 01:58:08.999
Fixed.

01:58:09.000 --> 01:58:10.999
I'd had one side turned down.

01:58:11.000 --> 01:58:11.999
What?

01:58:12.000 --> 01:58:21.999
You couldn't hear one speaker?

01:58:22.000 --> 01:58:32.999
It's working now, right?

01:58:33.000 --> 01:58:33.999
That sounds good.

01:58:34.000 --> 01:58:40.999
I think repeating it next
will make the idea come through.

01:58:41.000 --> 01:58:41.999
This one?

01:58:42.000 --> 01:58:42.999
Yes, that one.

01:58:43.000 --> 01:59:02.999
This part?

01:59:03.000 --> 01:59:11.999
Should we change the ending slightly?

01:59:12.000 --> 01:59:14.999
Maybe change it like this?

01:59:15.000 --> 01:59:15.999
Change the end? Where exactly?

01:59:16.000 --> 01:59:23.999
The chord changes slightly at the very end.

01:59:24.000 --> 01:59:24.999
Maybe like this...

01:59:25.000 --> 01:59:30.999
Then let's match it all the way through.

01:59:31.000 --> 01:59:31.999
Ah, just one.

01:59:32.000 --> 01:59:32.999
Nice.

01:59:33.000 --> 01:59:53.999
[Eunho tests the new line]

01:59:54.000 --> 01:59:56.999
Hit it once—nice, nice.

01:59:57.000 --> 01:59:57.999
It gives me butterflies.

01:59:58.000 --> 01:59:58.999
That was the wow moment.

01:59:59.000 --> 02:00:01.999
It was the wow moment.

02:00:02.000 --> 02:00:08.999
Use that last word later.

02:00:09.000 --> 02:00:10.999
Or use a word meaning ‘hold me back.’

02:00:11.000 --> 02:00:17.999
I might actually fly away,
so someone needs to hold me back.

02:00:18.000 --> 02:00:20.999
Okay, I'll record it, hyung.
Okay, okay.

02:00:21.000 --> 02:00:25.999
[Eunho records the revised line]

02:00:26.000 --> 02:00:26.999
[He repeats the final word]

02:00:27.000 --> 02:00:28.999
Okay, okay, okay.

02:00:29.000 --> 02:00:29.999
[He repeats the final word]

02:00:30.000 --> 02:00:30.999
I genuinely got goosebumps.

02:00:31.000 --> 02:00:31.999
Goosebumps.

02:00:32.000 --> 02:00:45.999
The good kind, right?

02:00:46.000 --> 02:00:52.999
Shall we trim it and listen?

02:00:53.000 --> 02:00:53.999
I think the recording sounds good.

02:00:54.000 --> 02:00:56.999
[They replay the recorded line]

02:00:57.000 --> 02:00:59.999
Start from the pre-chorus,
including the middle part.

02:01:00.000 --> 02:01:00.999
Hyung, look.

02:01:01.000 --> 02:01:01.999
Actually, play it from the beginning.

02:01:02.000 --> 02:01:02.999
I'll join in as it starts.

02:01:03.000 --> 02:01:03.999
From the beginning?

02:01:04.000 --> 02:01:21.999
From the pre-chorus.

02:01:22.000 --> 02:01:29.999
[They play the new pre-chorus]

02:01:30.000 --> 02:01:37.999
[The new song continues]

02:01:38.000 --> 02:01:43.999
[They sustain the final phrase]

02:01:44.000 --> 02:01:47.999
[They play the new chorus]

02:01:48.000 --> 02:01:54.999
[The chorus continues]

02:01:55.000 --> 02:01:56.999
That's good.

02:01:57.000 --> 02:01:57.999
That's good.

02:01:58.000 --> 02:01:58.999
This is good. Really good.

02:01:59.000 --> 02:01:59.999
Wait a second.

02:02:00.000 --> 02:02:00.999
It's so good.

02:02:01.000 --> 02:02:01.999
This is really, really good.

02:02:02.000 --> 02:02:02.999
How good are we talking?

02:02:03.000 --> 02:02:03.999
No, it just hit my ears...

02:02:04.000 --> 02:02:06.999
Whenever we produce on stream,
it turns out well.

02:02:07.000 --> 02:02:07.999
Wait. We need to talk.
What should we do?

02:02:08.000 --> 02:02:09.999
What do we do with this?

02:02:10.000 --> 02:02:11.999
What do we do?
I just got goosebumps.

02:02:12.000 --> 02:02:12.999
Wow, this came out so well. Seriously.

02:02:13.000 --> 02:02:14.999
I really like it.

02:02:15.000 --> 02:02:15.999
What do we do?

02:02:16.000 --> 02:02:16.999
Wait.

02:02:17.000 --> 02:02:17.999
No, this seriously came out so well.

02:02:18.000 --> 02:02:19.999
Everyone...

02:02:20.000 --> 02:02:20.999
it turned out incredibly well.

02:02:21.000 --> 02:02:21.999
What are we going to do?

02:02:22.000 --> 02:02:24.999
What now?

02:02:25.000 --> 02:02:28.999
Should we take today's stream down?

02:02:29.000 --> 02:02:30.999
This came out too well.

02:02:31.000 --> 02:02:31.999
What should we do?

02:02:32.000 --> 02:02:32.999
Wait a second.

02:02:33.000 --> 02:02:33.999
Let's hear it one more time.

02:02:34.000 --> 02:02:35.999
Just a second.

02:02:36.000 --> 02:02:58.999
It seriously turned out too well.

02:02:59.000 --> 02:03:09.999
[They replay the new pre-chorus]

02:03:10.000 --> 02:03:17.999
[They replay the new chorus]

02:03:18.000 --> 02:03:29.999
[The new song continues]

02:03:30.000 --> 02:03:32.999
[They replay the chorus]

02:03:33.000 --> 02:03:45.999
[The chorus continues]

02:03:46.000 --> 02:03:46.999
What are we going to do?

02:03:47.000 --> 02:03:47.999
What now?

02:03:48.000 --> 02:03:48.999
This is good.

02:03:49.000 --> 02:03:50.999
Good, good, good.

02:03:51.000 --> 02:03:51.999
It's seriously good. So good.

02:03:52.000 --> 02:03:52.999
We just discovered something, didn't we?

02:03:53.000 --> 02:03:54.999
Should we just go straight into the verse?

02:03:55.000 --> 02:03:55.999
What should we do?

02:03:56.000 --> 02:03:57.999
No, we can't do that already.

02:03:58.000 --> 02:03:59.999
Right. We can't do that yet.

02:04:00.000 --> 02:04:01.999
We can't reveal the whole thing.

02:04:02.000 --> 02:04:03.999
We don't know what we'll do with it yet.

02:04:04.000 --> 02:04:07.999
Should we add three-part harmony here?

02:04:08.000 --> 02:04:19.999
Let's try that.

02:04:20.000 --> 02:04:20.999
Would it sound cool if I sang it low?

02:04:21.000 --> 02:04:23.999
Really low here.

02:04:24.000 --> 02:04:28.999
Adding plenty of low harmony
would make it feel much more like a band.

02:04:29.000 --> 02:04:48.999
Okay, got it.
